Package: lcs
Version: 1.0.0-1~ubuntu24.04
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Petr Bena <petr@bena.rocks>
Installed-Size: 120
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.38), iproute2
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Description: Lightweight cluster service for quorum-managed VIPs
 lcs is a small Linux cluster service for quorum voting and safe virtual
 IP address ownership.
 .
 This package provides the lcs CLI, the lcsd daemon, and a systemd unit.
